Digital Lending supports the end-to-end lending lifecycle across all retail loan products and channels in a unified lending platform. Create a loan application process that suits the needs of your clients, both self-service application intake and assisted application intake.

New Invocable Actions
Get to know the invocable actions available with Digital lending for Financial Services Cloud.
New Apex Namespace in Digital Lending
The new industriesDigitalLending namespace has these new classes.
New Metadata Types in Digital Lending
Learn more about the new metadata types in Digital Lending.
Digital Lendingâ€”India
Support banks and financial institutions in India with an end-to-end loan origination solution.

Transaction Dispute Management
Streamline the dispute resolution process by integrating Transaction Dispute Management with Mastercom. Eliminate the inefficiencies that arise from switching between systems, ensure regulatory compliance, and reduce operational costs to enhance customer and employee experience.
Business Client Engagement
Your users can use Business Client Engagement to anticipate and fulfill the needs of their clients.

Rollup Definitions for Record Rollups
Use the Record Rollup Definitions feature to streamline the aggregation of records from various objects or groups and to provide a consolidated view of your data.
Integration Orchestration (Generally Available)
Review the status of the integration callouts by using Integration Orchestration.

Group Membership and Households
Use the Party Relationship Group data model to create groups or households easily and quickly. Organize your customers in convenient ways by using Groups or Households.

Data Cloud for Financial Services Cloud
Updates to Calculated Insights in Data Cloud and FlexCards in Salesforce to view more customer insights.
Capture Income and Expenses
View the cash inflow and outflow of your clients, identify spending trends, and prepare for upcoming client meetings.

Financial Account Management Standard Objects
Use Financial Account and related objects without installing the Financial Services Cloud managed package. Give your users greater control and flexibility over their data models.

Get Started Faster with Guided Setups
Discover the new guided setups for Financial Services Cloud.
Watch Financial Services Cloud Videos
New videos help your users with comprehensive guidance on the KYC data model and integrated onboarding in Financial Services Cloud.

Stage Management

With Stage Management, simplify complex business processes such as customer onboarding and transaction disputes with greater visibility and control.
